# Visual baselines (chromium-only)
#
# This directory holds the canonical PNG screenshots used by the
# `visual` Playwright project. To (re)generate baselines locally, run:
#
#     pnpm --filter apps-web run test:visual:update
#
# Baselines are committed alongside source. CI compares each run against the
# committed PNG with a `maxDiffPixelRatio` of 0.02. Cross-browser screenshots
# (e.g. webkit) are intentionally NOT captured here to avoid font-rendering
# drift; the project config locks the visual project to chromium only.
